fulltitle: SUN RA SPEAKS - PLANET GETTING WORSE / PLEIADES
description:
The interesting part of this video series is in many cases you get to hear Sunny (Sun Ra) speak his own thoughts about a particular subject which is featured in our music videos.

Sunny always spoke prophetically in which many of his visions have come true in the past, present an for the future. Next Sunny explains his composition Pleiades
